This is the area corresponding to the South Sea. This area is inspired from [[Phase 1/World 5|Phase 1]] 5-1 through 5-4.<br>
'''There are no repair docks on this hexagon, it will be necessary to move to the adjacent ones to be able to repair ships.<br>'''
:Fully clearing this area, alongside [[Kancolle Kai:Sandbox/Area 12#/V12-3|V12-3]] gives access to [[KanColle Kai:Sandbox/Area 12#/V12-4|V12-4]] ('''MI海域''').
:Clearing the second map of this area (V5-2), alongside [[Kancolle Kai:Sandbox/Area 3#/V3-4|V3-4]] gives access to [[KanColle Kai:Sandbox/Area 13#/V13-1|V13-1]] ('''AL海域''').
:Clearing the second map of this area (V5-2) gives access to [[KanColle Kai:Sandbox/Area 6#/V6-1|V6-1]] ('''中部海域''').
:Fully clearing this area, alongside [[Kancolle Kai:Sandbox/Area 4#/V4-1|V4-1]] gives access to [[KanColle Kai:Sandbox/Area 14#/V14-1|V14-1]] ('''FS海域''').

